    "en": {
      "name": "Skyfire of the Sacred Beast",
      "effect": "During your Main Phase: You can place 2 \"Skyfire of the Sacred Beast\" from your hand, Deck, and/or GY face-up on your field, then you can reveal 1 Level 10 \"Sacred Beast\" monster in your hand, then place 1 \"Fallen Paradise of the Sacred Beasts\" from your Deck face-up in your Field Zone. During your opponent's End Phase, if this card is in your GY: You can add it to your hand. You can only use each effect of \"Skyfire of the Sacred Beast\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
